2000-01-19  Ulf Betlehem  <flu@iki.fi>

	* cplay: Enter now plays files bypassing the playlist
	Space adds files to playlist
	a adds recursively
	z toggles pause
	x toggles stop
	m3u lines beginning with '#' are now silently discarded

